    • Field Detail

      • arc_stat

        public int[] arc_stat
        Integer array of size narcs=n*m. arc_stat[arc] of the arc i*n+j can be BASIC or NONBAS (or NONBASU if there are explicit capacities on arcs)

      • tree_p

        public int[] tree_p
        tree_p[node] = predecessor of node p in the basis tree

      • tree_t

        public int[] tree_t
        tree_t[node] = number of nodes in subtree of the basis tree rooted at node "node"

      • totalCost

        public double totalCost
        total cost of a basic solution

      • flow

        public int[] flow
        flow quantities in a basic solution: i.e. flow[arc] is the flow from supplier i to customer j on the arc i*n+j
